            <sp who="b">
               <p>Child.<lb/>
No: For the holy Ghost saith, <quote type="biblical" ana="Acts 4.12">There<lb/>
is no <normalised orig="saluation" auto="true">salvation</normalised> in any other, for among<lb/>
men there is <normalised orig="giuen" auto="true">given</normalised> no other name <normalised orig="vnder" auto="true">under</normalised><lb/>
                     <pb n="1"/>
                     <lb/>
<normalised orig="heauen" auto="true">heaven</normalised>, whereby we must be <normalised orig="saued" auto="true">saved</normalised>.</quote> And<lb/>
<normalised orig="againe" auto="true">again</normalised>, <quote type="biblical" ana="Acts 10.43">To him <normalised orig="doe" auto="true">do</normalised> all the Prophets <normalised orig="witnesse" auto="true">witness</normalised>,<lb/>
that through his name <normalised orig="onely" auto="true">only</normalised>, all<lb/>
that <normalised orig="beleeue" auto="true">believe</normalised> shall <normalised orig="receiue" auto="true">receive</normalised> remission of<lb/>
<normalised orig="sinne" auto="true">sin</normalised>.</quote>
                  <lb/>
                  <lb/>
               </p>
