What say you then to Popes pardons,<lb/>
Indulgences, Masses, <notvariant>Trentales</notvariant>,<lb/>
Dirges, and such like: May not a man<lb/>
by them <normalised orig="obtaine" auto="true">obtain</normalised> remission of <normalised orig="sinnes" auto="true">sins</normalised>,<lb/>
and <normalised orig="eternall" auto="true">eternal</normalised> life?<lb/>
               </p>
