            <sp who="b">
               <p>Child.<lb/>
Nothing <normalised orig="lesse" auto="true">less</normalised>: For the Scripture<lb/>
<normalised orig="knoweth" auto="true">knows</normalised> no such <normalised orig="meanes" auto="true">means</normalised> or <normalised orig="wayes" auto="true">ways</normalised><lb/>
to <normalised orig="eternall" auto="true">eternal</normalised> life: but <normalised orig="doth" auto="false">does</normalised> <normalised orig="vtterly" auto="true">utterly</normalised> <normalised orig="reiect" auto="true">reject</normalised><lb/>
them as most <normalised orig="abhominable" auto="true">abominable</normalised> <normalised orig="deuises" auto="true">devises</normalised><lb/>
of them.<lb/>
