            <sp who="a">
               <p>Father.<lb/>
                  <lb/>
If wee cannot <normalised orig="bee" auto="true">be</normalised> <normalised orig="saued" auto="true">saved</normalised> by works,<lb/>
then wherefore should wee <normalised orig="doe" auto="true">do</normalised> them?<lb/>
as good play for <normalised orig="naught" auto="true">nought</normalised>, as <normalised orig="worke" auto="true">work</normalised> for<lb/>
<normalised orig="naught" auto="true">nought</normalised>?<lb/>
               </p>
