            <sp who="b">
               <p>Child.<lb/>
No <normalised orig="worke" auto="true">work</normalised> of man is sound and<lb/>
currant <normalised orig="indeede" auto="true">indeed</normalised>, except the same <normalised orig="bee" auto="true">be</normalised><lb/>
<normalised orig="commaunded" auto="true">commanded</normalised> of God to <normalised orig="bee" auto="true">be</normalised> done: and<lb/>
