and manner as <normalised orig="hee" auto="true">he</normalised> <normalised orig="requireth" auto="true">requires</normalised>, that is,<lb/>
from a <normalised orig="carefull" auto="true">careful</normalised> heart, and sanctified<lb/>
mind: otherwise, <normalised orig="whatsoeuer" auto="true">whatsoever</normalised> wee do<lb/>
