None <normalised orig="shalbee" auto="true">shall be</normalised> <normalised orig="saued" auto="true">saved</normalised> by Christ, but<lb/>
<normalised orig="onely" auto="true">only</normalised> such as <normalised orig="beleeue" auto="true">believe</normalised> in Christ, that<lb/>
